---
import Container from "@components/Container.astro";
import Footer from "@components/Footer.astro";
import GetAppButton from "@components/GetAppButton.astro";
import Page from "@layouts/Page.astro";
---

<Page
  title="2024's Best Workout Timers for iPhone - Box Timer"
  description="Workout timers are essential for sessions both at the gym and at home. Here's a comparison of the top five workout timer apps available in 2024."
  url="https://boxtimer.app/2024-best-workout-timers-iphone/"
>
  <Container innerClass={"flex-col items-center"}>
    <div class="w-full sm:w-9/12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-sans font-bold">
        2024's Best Workout Timers for iPhone
      </h2>
      <p class="py-8">
        A workout timer is essential whether you're at the gym, home, or
        outdoors. It keeps your exercises structured, motivates you, and ensures
        efficiency. In any setting, it helps maintain focus, optimizes
        performance, and facilitates seamless transitions between exercises,
        enhancing the overall quality of your workout routine.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-32">
        Here's a comparison of the top five workout timer apps available in
        2024.
      </p>

      <div class="flex justify-start items-center">
        <img
          class="rounded-lg w-16 h-16 mr-8 border-[2px] border-zinc-800"
          src="/images/box-timer-workout-timer-icon.webp"
          alt="Box Timer - Workout Timer - App Icon"
        />
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-sans font-bold">
          1. Box Timer - Workout Timer
        </h3>
      </div>

      <p class="py-8">
        Box Timer offers a versatile and customizable workout timer experience.
        With its intuitive interface, it allows users to create and personalize
        timers for various workout routines like HIIT, Tabata, and more. Its
        audio and visual cues keep users on track during their sessions.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        <b>Key Features</b>
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc ml-8 mb-8">
        <li>Customizable timers for different workout styles</li>
        <li>Audio and visual cues for intervals</li>
        <li>Minimalistic and user-friendly design</li>
        <li>Free</li>
        <li>No ads</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-32">
        <a
          class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
          href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/box-timer-workout-timer/id1547518531"
          target="_blank"
          onclick="window.fathom.trackGoal('GTWFCG7B', 0);"
          >Get Box Timer - Workout timer at the App Store</a
        >
      </p>

      <div class="flex justify-start items-center">
        <img
          class="rounded-lg w-16 h-16 mr-8"
          src="/images/interval-timer-hiit-workout-icon.webp"
          alt="Interval Timer - HIIT Workouts - App Icon"
        />
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-sans font-bold">
          2. Interval Timer - HIIT Workouts
        </h3>
      </div>
      <p class="py-8">
        This app is tailored specifically for HIIT workouts. It allows users to
        create intervals with different durations and exercises. With a clean
        design and easy-to-use interface, it helps users stay focused during
        high-intensity sessions.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        <b>Key Features</b>
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-8 mb-8">
        <li>HIIT-focused timer</li>
        <li>Customizable intervals and exercises</li>
        <li>Clean and simple design</li>
        <li>Free but with in-app purchases</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-32">
        <a
          class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
          href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/interval-timer-hiit-timer/id1124297113"
          target="_blank"
          onclick="window.fathom.trackEvent('Link to Interval Timer - HIIT Workouts');"
          >Get Interval Timer - HIIT Workouts at the App Store</a
        >
      </p>

      <div class="flex justify-start items-center">
        <img
          class="rounded-lg w-16 h-16 mr-8"
          src="/images/tabata-timer-interval-timer-icon.webp"
          alt="Tabata Timer: Interval Timer - App Icon"
        />
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-sans font-bold">
          3. Tabata Timer: Interval Timer
        </h3>
      </div>

      <p class="py-8">
        Tabata Timer is dedicated to the Tabata workout style, popular for its
        short bursts of intense exercise followed by brief rests. The app offers
        preset timers and customizable options, making it a favorite among those
        who follow this particular training regimen.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        <b>Key Features</b>
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-8 mb-8">
        <li>Specialized for Tabata workouts</li>
        <li>Preset timers and customization options</li>
        <li>User-friendly interface</li>
        <li>Free but with in-app purchases</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-32">
        <a
          class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
          href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/tabata-timer-interval-timer/id1255964203"
          target="_blank"
          onclick="window.fathom.trackEvent('Link to Tabata Timer: Interval Timer');"
          >Get Tabata Timer: Interval Timer at the App Store</a
        >
      </p>

      <div class="flex justify-start items-center">
        <img
          class="rounded-lg w-16 h-16 mr-8"
          src="/images/seconds-pro-interval-timer-icon.webp"
          alt="Seconds Pro Interval Timer - App Icon"
        />
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-sans font-bold">
          4. Seconds Pro Interval Timer
        </h3>
      </div>
      <p class="py-8">
        Seconds Pro is a comprehensive interval timer suitable for various
        workouts, from circuit training to yoga. It includes templates and
        customizable timers, allowing users to create personalized routines. The
        app's flexibility and range make it a versatile choice for fitness
        enthusiasts.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        <b>Key Features</b>
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-8 mb-8">
        <li>Versatile for different workout types</li>
        <li>Templates and customization options</li>
        <li>Adaptable for various fitness levels</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-32">
        <a
          class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
          href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/seconds-pro-interval-timer/id363978811"
          target="_blank"
          onclick="window.fathom.trackEvent('Link to Seconds Pro Interval Timer');"
          >Get Seconds Pro Interval Timer at the App Store</a
        >
      </p>

      <div class="flex justify-start items-center">
        <img
          class="rounded-lg w-16 h-16 mr-8 border-[2px] border-zinc-800"
          src="/images/tabata-stopwatch-pro-icon.webp"
          alt="Tabata Stopwatch Pro - App Icon"
        />
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-sans font-bold">5. Tabata Stopwatch Pro</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="py-8">
        Another app focused on HIIT and Tabata workouts, this timer emphasizes
        simplicity and ease of use. It offers preset routines and allows users
        to create custom intervals, making it suitable for both beginners and
        experienced athletes.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        <b>Key Features</b>
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-8 mb-8">
        <li>Emphasis on simplicity</li>
        <li>Pre-designed routines and custom intervals</li>
        <li>Suitable for all levels of fitness</li>
        <li>Free but with in-app purchases</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-32">
        <a
          class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
          href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/tabata-timer-and-hiit-timer/id664563975"
          target="_blank"
          onclick="window.fathom.trackEvent('Link to Tabata Stopwatch Pro');"
          >Get Workout Timer: HIIT & Tabata at the App Store</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
    <Footer />
  </Container>
</Page>
